Describes a road part of a route.

ItemTypes::entryrestriction_t  negEntryrestr = ItemTypes::noRestrictions
) 
 

Creates a new ExpandedRouteRoadItem.

Parameters:
mapID The map id of the road.
nodeID The node id of the road.
roadClass The class of the road, from major road to fourth class road.
roadName The name(s) of the road, the ownership is transfered to this class.
posSpeedLimit The speed limit in positive direction (first -> last coordinate). MAX_UINT32 is unknown speedlimit.
negSpeedLimit The speed limit in negative direction (last -> first coordinate). MAX_UINT32 is unknown speedlimit.
multidigitialized True if this road is multidigitalized, false otherwise.
ramp True if this road is a ramp, false otherwise.
roundabout True if this road is part of a roundabout, false otherwise.
controlledAccess True if road access ways are controlled.
turn True if this road is the turn.
driveOnRightSide If to drive on the right side of the road.
startLevel The level, relative ground, of the first coordinate.
endLevel The level, relative ground, of the last coordinate.
posEntryrestr The entry restrictions when entering the road at first ccordinate.
negEntryrestr The entry restrictions when entering the road at last coordinate.
